  <brief_title>Phase III Randomized Study of SYNSORB Pk in Children With E. Coli-Associated Hemolytic Uremic Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase III Randomized Study of SYNSORB Pk in Children With E. Coli-Associated</official_title>
